This directory contains source and objects for banners, a collection
of banner writing programs.

Program:	banner-01 to 13
Revision:	
Author:		various
Date ported:	9 September 1993
Ported by:	Greg Lehey, LEMIS
Compiler used:	gcc-2.4.5

Prerequisites:	none

Documentation:	README file, copied to man page banner

Installation:	

Comments:	Comments in the file ../README.LEMIS are not repeated
		here. You should read ../README.LEMIS first.

Modifications:

0. No configuration. Modify Makefile to add clean and install targets.

1. Remove banner 10 from default list: it needs a Pascal compiler.

2. Banner 3 died with undefined rindex. Define as strrchr.

3. Banner 11 omitted due to complictions with the fonts.